<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231175>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Minutomon shanweiense, new genus, new species, male holotype (13.4 × 10.8 mm) (SYSU 001126). A, dorsal overall view; B, ventral view showing anterior thoracic sternum and abdomen; C, frontal view of carapace; D, ventral view showing sterno-abdominal cavity with right G 1 in situ (left G 1 removed)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231175/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231176>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Minutomon shanweiense, new genus, new species, male holotype (13.4 × 10.8 mm) (SYSU 001126). A, left G 2; B, left G 1 (ventral view); C, G 1 terminal segment (ventral view); D, left third maxilliped. (white bar = 1.0 mm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231176/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

